Package: DTAtoolkit
Type: Package
Title: Diagnostic Test Accuracy Meta-Analysis Toolkit
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(
    given = "Payam",
    family = "PJD",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "payampjd2000@gmail.com"
  )
Description: Streamlined workflows for meta-analysis of diagnostic test
    accuracy using study-level two-by-two tables. The package supports
    bivariate Reitsma models, sensitivity and specificity forest plots,
    summary receiver operating characteristic curves, likelihood-ratio
    matrices, Fagan nomograms, subgroup comparisons, influential-study
    analysis, bootstrap inference, and publication-bias diagnostics.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/Payam-PJD/DTAtoolkit
